00:56:53.080 --> 00:56:56.679
is, um, imposter syndrome mitigation.

00:56:56.679 --> 00:57:02.120
I feel like there's a really big veil of mystery that's like drawn over data science

00:57:02.120 --> 00:57:07.239
jobs because we maybe don't speak to each other about what we do on a daily basis.

00:57:07.239 --> 00:57:09.479
Like, I don't know what all these other people do.

00:57:09.479 --> 00:57:13.239
